  <brief_title>Magnesium Sulphate Versus Lidocaine for Control of Emergence Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>Control of Emergence Hypertension After Craniotomy: Comparison Between the Efficacy of Magnesium Sulphate and Lidocaine Infusion (Randomized Controlled Study)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
